OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781923667
OL,3,CConjoined twins separated after 40
OL,4,Chours of operations
OL,6,FConjoined twin sisters have been
OL,7,Fseparated by a team of British
OL,8,Fsurgeons after a series of
OL,9,F"groundbreaking" operations.
OL,11,FMercy and Goodness were born in Ekiti,
OL,12,Fsouth-western Nigeria, with fused
OL,13,Fskulls, shared brain tissue and blood
OL,14,Fvessels - which is a rare condition
OL,15,Fcalled craniopagus twinning.
OL,17,FAt six months, they were referred to
OL,18,FBritish charity Gemini Untwined, the
OL,19,Fonly organisation in the world that
OL,20,Ffocuses on research and operations for
OL,21,Fcraniopagus twins.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
