FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781923667
OL,3,CConjoined twins separated after 40
OL,4,Chours of operations
OL,6,FAfter extensive planning, the twins
OL,7,Ftraveled to Abu Dhabi in the United
OL,8,FArab Emirates last year for treatment
OL,9,Fat the SEHA Sheikh Khalifa Medical
OL,10,FCity.
OL,12,FA team of more than 60 surgeons from
OL,13,Ffour countries, including the UK,
OL,14,Fperformed a series of procedures over
OL,15,Ffour months, with the final surgery
OL,16,Flasting a total of 12 hours.
OL,18,FMercy and Goodness have since made a
OL,19,Ffull recovery and will be returning
OL,20,Fhome to Nigeria.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781923667
OL,3,CConjoined twins separated after 40
OL,4,Chours of operations
OL,6,FThe surgery is one of the most complex
OL,7,Fof its kind, and was only the ninth
OL,8,Fsuccessful separation of craniopagus
OL,9,Ftwins undertaken by Gemini Untwined.
OL,11,FThe charity said the operations
OL,12,Fincluded several new and refined
OL,13,Ftechniques, including an 'Open Book'
OL,14,Fapproach, which uses gravity to
OL,15,Fsupport the brain during surgery
OL,16,Frather than traditional retractors,
OL,17,Fhelping to reduce pressure and
OL,18,Fpotential trauma.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
