OL,3,CConjoined twins separated after 40
OL,4,Chours of operations
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIn the months leading up to the final
OL,12,Fprocedure, the team used a combination
OL,13,Fof 3D imaging, virtual reality
OL,14,Fsimulation, augmented overlays, and
OL,15,Fultrasound-guided expansion to map the
OL,16,Ftwins' anatomy in detail.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
