PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1781923667
OL,3,CConjoined twins separated after 40
OL,4,Chours of operations
OL,6,FConjoined twins are extremely rare,
OL,7,Fonly occurring one in every 2.5
OL,8,Fmillion births and only 5% of these
OL,9,Fare craniopagus, like Mercy and
OL,10,FGoodness.
OL,12,FThe chance of craniopagus twins
OL,13,Fundergoing surgery is even more
OL,14,Funlikely, at around one in 10 million
OL,15,Fbirths.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
